  "verification_notes": "HELD — WRONG REGION. 1golf.eu confirms 'Prapasri Golf Course' is located at Kridsrivara Camp, Sakon Nakhon, Thailand — a military camp course in the northeastern province of Sakon Nakhon, approximately 650 km from Bangkok. This is not a Bangkok-area course. The course is a 9-hole, par-36 military/public facility with green fees of approximately 120 THB. The 4moles.com listing for 'Royal Thai Army Prapasri Golf Club' also places it outside Bangkok. It is possible the pipeline brief intended a different 'Prapasri' location (possibly the Royal Thai Army Prapasri Golf Club in Bangkok proper), but no second 'Prapasri' course has been identified near Bangkok in any database searched. Recommend flagging to pipeline coordinator for clarification. Do not publish.",
